{"tid":1992592,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果冇捍衛本土文化","createTime":"2020-04-28T08:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T04:47:31.000Z","uid":223799,"like":14,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f9e398430a923aa1d21839858447a1fa2a8014","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"蘋果終於用返「二奶」唔用乜𠹌柒「小三」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1991579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1991579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 講蘋果用返二奶唔用小三，呢個係進步，但蘋果絕對冇捍衛廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n留意呢個post 唔係鬥黃，依家訂蘋果係呢一刻最務實嘅嘢，但捍衛廣東話應該係寫粵文，唔係寫中文。<br />\n<br />\n「書面語」唔等於廣東話，佢只係中文嘅延伸，最多你可以叫佢港式中文。<br />\n<br />\n語言係身份認同入面好重要嘅一部份，發展粵文就等於發展香港人嘅身份同文化，但依家粵文嘅語料實在太少，地位又因為政策比中文低，如果有份報紙全面用粵文，就係粵文地位提升嘅一個里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n講多次，蘋果冇捍衛本土文化，要分清咩係粵文同中文。<br />\n<br />\n利申：男朋友做毒果，講極都唔肯寫粵文，我屌佢老母"},{"pid":"47c1e9c61240360f0d46d1f4b4d5b33afc5fa047","tid":1992592,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"一步步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb5442d6f19b9eb6c6d873cf5b2ee18c9e9a4a2","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c1e9c61240360f0d46d1f4b4d5b33afc5fa047","tid":1992592,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"一步步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"有報紙行第一步差好遠"},{"pid":"d7b32834cc65c69ec0baf28ca7c9acd44e6de195","tid":1992592,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"以前報紙佬唔係寫粵文<br />\n但寫得好文雅 （唔知點講 總之睇得又似文言又似白話咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n我覺得記者要改善下文筆<br />\n粵文既話 一步步黎啦"},{"pid":"83fc578b347064a919bf39a3b4e3edc9fd2e4227","tid":1992592,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申：男朋友做毒果，講極都唔肯寫粵文，我屌佢老母</blockquote><br />\n點解佢咁堅持先?<br />\n<br />\n怕高層壓力, 唔敢擅作主張?<br />\n定抑或佢本身個觀念係睇唔起粵文?"},{"pid":"188a88c2a7e5a233a456828f802837a8f0814e91","tid":1992592,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0bbb9bab8b4bd240ff8faf2f4955474c4be0228","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83fc578b347064a919bf39a3b4e3edc9fd2e4227","tid":1992592,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申：男朋友做毒果，講極都唔肯寫粵文，我屌佢老母</blockquote><br />\n點解佢咁堅持先?<br />\n<br />\n怕高層壓力, 唔敢擅作主張?<br />\n定抑或佢本身個觀念係睇唔起粵文?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"以我所知編輯冇畀過壓力，觀念我諗係主要原因。接受香港教育，好多時就會覺得粵文係錯"},{"pid":"ca77c78062f8b8a7a9239f8c007ec505275cf4cb","tid":1992592,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:59:21.000Z","msg":"粵文 笑到抽筋"},{"pid":"c055931fcf2d515cc52c768f35f68213e66ff58f","tid":1992592,"uid":102997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"其實粵文唔係本土文化 係新文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b580df069583b15c3c5f468aacd22ddb523fb873","tid":1992592,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b32834cc65c69ec0baf28ca7c9acd44e6de195","tid":1992592,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"以前報紙佬唔係寫粵文<br />\n但寫得好文雅 （唔知點講 總之睇得又似文言又似白話咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n我覺得記者要改善下文筆<br />\n粵文既話 一步步黎啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"三及第<br />\n文言文 白話文 粵文<br />\n呢個先係由來已久嘅本土書寫方式"},{"pid":"a09d61599646c6167ab3a8b0865b79127