me":"2020-04-28T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"不嬲呢D方言係唔會用黎寫文章<br />\n台灣人都唔會用台語書寫啦"},{"pid":"db1d5cc46c4244d424655016b1d092714bd6623e","tid":1992592,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd2ebb37cbb8766726a57a9908162ea3d229ba4","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"550adcc03965eba32f2c50e0db78110b5eefa32c","tid":1992592,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5cc4d62fc6a747f4137ec411eaec37e563aad62","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"錯，錯晒，書面語根本就係中文唔係粵文，唔好混淆兩種語言。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"粵文何以代表香港本土文化？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"你噉問，同問韓文點解代表韓國文化，日文點解代表日本文化一樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"所以樓主意思喺廣東等於香港，香港等於廣東？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，樓主喺唔喺當書面語嘅香港文學全部冇到？"},{"pid":"bb0b57db4a28c30f55953e961ac0f8d6b5ce671d","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"db1d5cc46c4244d424655016b1d092714bd6623e","tid":1992592,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd2ebb37cbb8766726a57a9908162ea3d229ba4","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"550adcc03965eba32f2c50e0db78110b5eefa32c","tid":1992592,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"粵文何以代表香港本土文化？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"你噉問，同問韓文點解代表韓國文化，日文點解代表日本文化一樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"所以樓主意思喺廣東等於香港，香港等於廣東？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，樓主喺唔喺當書面語嘅香港文學全部冇到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"我當佢哋係中國文學，唔係香港文學。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅用字係粵文，唔係廣東話。香港同廣東完全唔一樣。"},{"pid":"c9a78e1049ed007c160c31a85f6a7bf5c7e66789","tid":1992592,"uid":135040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"Sor lor 唔夠黃，批鬥得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1733ce98810231635b739993ac434f7b65d8e3fa","tid":1992592,"uid":201031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"拎返以前啲報紙睇<br />\n再睇返而家簡直垃圾<br />\n冇個記者合格"},{"pid":"e31ac1578d8aafd6ab017b2eac82b3c7552d173c","tid":1992592,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d2d70eb357d18a4b30194779f6a689a4663a21c","tid":1992592,"uid":266172,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"其實由細到大都係作文用書面語，你要人寫廣東話應該係你年紀太細，唔知以前香港係點，以為有人寫廣東話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"關於粵語書寫歷史同前境可以睇吓呢篇文章：<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@chaaak/寫廣東話嘅路-應該點行落去-9e66dfb8f354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40chaaak%2F%E5%AF%AB%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A9%B1%E5%98%85%E8%B7%AF-%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E9%BB%9E%E8%A1%8C%E8%90%BD%E5%8E%BB-9e66dfb8f354&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=f84854be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@chaaak/寫廣東話嘅路-應該點行落去-9e66dfb8f354</a>"},{"pid":"5856d36c8f181f1a7fa1a7e89937fc93acbf809c","tid":1992592,"uid":188104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"仲有呢一篇係粵文維基百科其中一個創始管理員寫嘅：<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/2184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F2184&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=3dc2dfc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/2184</a><br />\n<br />\n一種書寫語言大家用慣咗，突然要去改變未必係易接受，但唔代表要否定佢嘅價值。廣東話係每個字都可以寫出嚟，但香港人連「比、俾、畀」都未分到，作為香港人其實都應該反思一下，喺保育自己嘅語言同文字上，係唔係已經盡力"},{"pid":"eb166e1f40caec033c3aa6b8608d3b8d5e6a3ec7","tid":1992592,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0b57db4a28c30f55953e961ac0f8d6b5ce671d","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"db1d5cc46c4244d424655016b1d092714bd6623e","tid":1992592,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd2ebb37cbb8766726a57a9908162ea3d229ba4","tid":1992592,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"你噉問，同問韓文點解代表韓國文化，日文點解代表日本文化一樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"所以樓主意思喺廣東等於香港，香港等於廣東？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，樓主喺唔喺當書面語嘅香港文學全部冇到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"我當佢哋係中國文學，唔係香港文學。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅用字係粵文，唔係廣東話。香港同廣東完全唔一樣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"嗰啲又真係香港文學，不過可以再細分為「香港白話文學」同「香港粵文文學」？<br />\n<br />\n尤其係好多作家好似劉以鬯咁，佢嘅文學係由香港人嘅思緒同時代背景出發，如果被排除喺香港文學之外，實在講唔通"}]}